    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091270/extras/daa2988a7a686d9f3b47ae27c848bcaf.poster.avif?t=1722327272\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091270/extras/daa2988a7a686d9f3b47ae27c848bcaf.webm?t=1722327272\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091270/extras/daa2988a7a686d9f3b47ae27c848bcaf.mp4?t=1722327272\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About This Game</h2><strong>&quot;Survive the ghostly horrors until the end&quot;</strong><br><strong>Ghost Jumper </strong>is a 2D action casual game where you survive by avoiding ghosts in a haunted forest. It features simple but addictive gameplay and easy-to-learn controls that make it highly immersive. While the controls are simple, the game itself is not. With challenging difficulty and gameplay, along with cute and emotional atmosphere, you can deeply immerse yourself in the game.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091270/extras/2249d09cb1d86154e2d60ccbf8eb561f.poster.avif?t=1722327272\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091270/extras/2249d09cb1d86154e2d60ccbf8eb561f.webm?t=1722327272\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091270/extras/2249d09cb1d86154e2d60ccbf8eb561f.mp4?t=1722327272\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Red Hood</h2>Enter a world inspired by fairy tales with charming graphics. Instead of the classic young girl with a red hood, you will play as a cute and lovable wolf.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091270/extras/ee5fae28aec2b17bfb948e7ea9cbb369.avif?t=1722327272\" width=600 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Haunted Forest</h2>Our furry red hood has lost its way in a forest full of ghosts. Can you help Red Hood escape this eerie forest?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091270/extras/52ab3f6a981a0c508961128dd4dcc7e5.poster.avif?t=1722327272\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091270/extras/52ab3f6a981a0c508961128dd4dcc7e5.webm?t=1722327272\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091270/extras/52ab3f6a981a0c508961128dd4dcc7e5.mp4?t=1722327272\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Angry Ghosts</h2>As your score increases, the ghosts become more aggressive. Overcome the increasing difficulty and set a new record.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >New Records</h2>Every game offers a new experience to beat your high score. Compete with other players and boost your competitive spirit.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091270/extras/61773a1c05ada1125dfd2aa1debf99eb.avif?t=1722327272\" width=600 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Simple Controls</h2>Controls are very simple. Move. Jump. Double Jump. Enjoy the captivating simplicity of this game!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >System Requirements</h2>'Ghost Jumper' can be played on PCs running Windows.",
